Jeremiah Meaghar, Acting Consul at Lisbon to the Board. Has incurred expenditure in supporting destitute crew members of the St. Helena, Margaret, Velocity and Amelia, seized by the Portuguese blockading squadron off Terceira, the Azores. The crews have been transported to the Tagus in the Diana frigate but Mr. Mackenzie has been unable to obtain restitution from the Portuguese government.
